metadata.name: Beauty
metadata.description: Beauty - Behind our daily masks and the years which pass and overtake us, the thread of the gaze is the replica of what is woven in our hearts and connects us beyond the wall of the skin. The most beautiful of all piercings remains the one that our lips display to mark this moment of youth when we looked like Beauty and the Beast, united by the magic of this sorcerer of all tales: the Love that is woven in our eyes and makes fall our masks.
